{"tid":531092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沒用英文正楷填表 4港大生參選學生會被DQ","createTime":"2018-01-16T12:23:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-16T12:54:40.000Z","uid":5195,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3c0302cf814d5faf979d33ad75f3ec3f2a42692a","tid":531092,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T12:23:28.000Z","msg":"新一屆港大學生會面臨「缺莊」危機，最近更觸發「DQ」爭議，4名學生在截止時間前趕及遞交參選表格，惟隨後被學生會選舉委員會以沒用「正楷（BLOCK LETTERS）」填表及學科資料出錯等原因，裁定4人參選無效。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被DQ的內閣成員今日召開記者會，確認4名成員被取消參選資格，其中一名成員表示不猜測學生會的動機，促請學生會作出解釋。不過，會見記者的兩名成員多次迴避問題，被問及內閣是否與中聯辦有關係時，他們回應指：「唔知同中聯辦有關聯嘅消息喺邊度嚟？」"},{"pid":"328514ef44d7f3f72b7ffa6703a3f629900eeeff","tid":531092,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T12:29:23.000Z","msg":"咁可疑?"},{"pid":"160765b7a4fca92f1875b428a53146ed4f8562e2","tid":531092,"uid":11001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T12:51:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkucampustv/videos/1595886650480025/?comment_id=1595943313807692\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkucampustv%2Fvideos%2F1595886650480025%2F%3Fcomment_id%3D1595943313807692&d=1XqBj0AsuG9BAg1bToNApdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=f7525128\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkucampustv/videos/1595886650480025/?comment_id=1595943313807692</a><br />\n<br />\n馮煒光同雪廠驊開聲撐，會係咩人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5055bf18f55b10a822c179630ee7f92411b4b65","tid":531092,"uid":163916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T12:54:40.000Z","msg":"衰過689<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}